    {
      "id": "PopularPost240734",
      "post_content": "I agree, this cards art is pretty cool, and I usually don't care for card art.  \n  \nMechanically, [Raise Dead](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Raise Dead) = ![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol).  \n[Chainer's Edict](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chainer's Edict)= ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol)  \nThis = ![4](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=4&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol)??? I mean I realize it would have to cost a little more than ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol), but still.  \n  \nAnd I don't mean to offend lorendorky, but your comment was rather ignorant. A card does not have to be mythic rare to be good. Counterpoint: [Archangel's Light](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Archangel's Light).  ",
      "posted_by": "pedrodyl",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost240734\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">I agree, this cards art is pretty cool, and I usually don't care for card art.<br/><br/>Mechanically, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Raise Dead\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Raise Dead\">Raise Dead</a> = <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/>.<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Chainer's Edict\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chainer's Edict\">Chainer's Edict</a>= <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/><br/>This = <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"4\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=4&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/>??? I mean I realize it would have to cost a little more than <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/>, but still.<br/><br/>And I don't mean to offend lorendorky, but your comment was rather ignorant. A card does not have to be mythic rare to be good. Counterpoint: <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Archangel's Light\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Archangel's Light\">Archangel's Light</a>.<br/></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '240734'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy67105\">pedrodyl</span>\r\n                                (4/27/2012 6:04:00 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"