    {
      "id": "PopularPost241235",
      "post_content": "Commons are not designed to be underpowered, they are designed to be the Bread and Butter of a limited format. They are basic but effective. Saying it's expensive because it's common makes no sense as there are plenty of cards in this set that are very powerful and aggressively priced at common, [Mist Raven](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mist Raven) being a prime example. I would say that an appropriate cost for this would be either ![2](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=2&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol) or ![3](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=3&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol), being ![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol) for a [Raise Dead](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Raise Dead), ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol)![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol) for a [Cruel Edict](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cruel Edict), ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol) to have both effects on one card, and ![0](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=0&type=symbol) or ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol) to allow the sacrificing to target any player. 2/5.",
      "posted_by": "Mickacabra",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost241235\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">Commons are not designed to be underpowered, they are designed to be the Bread and Butter of a limited format. They are basic but effective. Saying it's expensive because it's common makes no sense as there are plenty of cards in this set that are very powerful and aggressively priced at common, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mist Raven\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mist Raven\">Mist Raven</a> being a prime example. I would say that an appropriate cost for this would be either <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"2\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=2&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/> or <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"3\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=3&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/>, being <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/> for a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Raise Dead\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Raise Dead\">Raise Dead</a>, <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/> for a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Cruel Edict\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cruel Edict\">Cruel Edict</a>, <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/> to have both effects on one card, and <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"0\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=0&amp;type=symbol\"/> or <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/> to allow the sacrificing to target any player. 2/5.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '241235'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy46251\">Mickacabra</span>\r\n                                (4/28/2012 8:40:21 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Star