      "id": "PopularPost240556",
      "post_content": "@lorendorky  \nJust because a card is common shouldn't mean that it has to be terrible.  \nJust look at [Doomed Traveler](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Doomed Traveler) or [Delver of Secrets](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Delver of Secrets) or even [Lightning Bolt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt).  \nThis card would have been perfectly reasonable at 1BB or 2BB and a sorcery, putting it at 6 mana is a travesty.  \nBut honestly, who cares about what the card does, the art is gorgeous.",
