      "id": "PopularPost242124",
      "post_content": "I'll restate my opinion from the forums: There is no excuse for printing this card at 6 mana. [Cruel Revival](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cruel Revival) allowed targeted, near-unconditional INSTANT-SPEED removal at 5 mana. It was printed in Onslaught (Back when removal was quite a bit worse than it is now), and it was still terrible. There is no excuse for Grave Exchange being so over-costed beyond \"Bad cards need to exist, because we want new players to be unable to play their decks at FNMs due to all the terrible cards we slip into packs and precons.\"",
      "posted_by": "Fireballmage",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost242124\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_post\">I'll restate my opinion from the forums: There is no excuse for printing this card at 6 mana. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Cruel Revival\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Cruel Revival\">Cruel Revival</a> allowed targeted, near-unconditional INSTANT-SPEED removal at 5 mana. It was printed in Onslaught (Back when removal was quite a bit worse than it is now), and it was still terrible. There is no excuse for Grave Exchange being so over-costed beyond \"Bad cards need to exist, because we want new players to be unable to play their decks at FNMs due to all the terrible cards we slip into packs and precons.\"</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '242124'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy81627\">Fireballmage</span>\r\n                                (4/30/2012 4:47:37 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_po